            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Shares the sanitized sample text, category, model version, and a coarse language/region tag (e.g. zh-CN) via iCloud. No sender, account, or device identifiers are sent. Requires an iCloud session; a receipt lets you delete your latest submission."
